Description:

URL finder for HbbTV

Use the vdr-plugin-dsmcc for receive carousel objects (https://github.com/ua0lnj/vdr-plugin-dsmcc).
For browser as example, use chromium and hbbtv plugin (https://github.com/karl-rousseau/HybridTvViewer).

